race.description: Tabtouch - Have You Got The Touch Hcp (C5)
race.comment: Tough. MANTUA (1) was doing his best work late getting up for third over 1200m at Ascot. Missed a whisker there prior over this shorter sprint and draws for a softer run today. Comes back in grade and is a decent chance. UNDER INFLUENCE (3) has raced at Ascot his last two and will find this more suitable. The shorter sprint shouldn't be an issue, and he has an inside barrier and CJP aboard. His best is good enough. AIN'TSOBAD (4) has been racing at Ascot and two back was only beaten 2.2L after settling back from a cruel barrier. Maps well today and has a 2kg claim. Has to drop back 400m but should be finishing hard. PRINCE AMONGST MEN (12) races forward and has been going well in the country. Led and just missed this grade here three back so has the ability. Something for the Multiples: UNIVERSAL PLAYBOY (6)
